  <entry>
    <title>【PC,KR】白日梦的构想图</title>
    <link href="https://yinghu.netlify.app/posts/5863bf98.html"/>
    <id>https://yinghu.netlify.app/posts/5863bf98.html</id>
    <published>2024-05-25T04:01:18.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-05-25T04:16:04.972Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>有岛芳是45岁的代课教师。</p><p>曾立志成为作家的他，因感慨与大学时代遇到的学长波多野秋房，无论是创作能力，或是人格魅力都判若云泥，遂放弃了梦想。</p><p>如今忍受着作为编辑的妻子侮蔑的眼神，每天过着平淡无奇的生活。</p><p>某天，有岛大学时代的研讨会教授乘鹤西去。<br>在悼念会上，有岛看到了自己工作的学校的学生身影。</p><p>这位女学生・波多野凛，正是大学时代浇灭有岛梦想的波多野秋房的令女。</p><p>自悼念会后，有岛与凛开始在图书馆三言两语交流。</p><p>「我想读你写的文章」</p><p>凛向有岛抛出的话语，正是妻子曾经说过的话。</p><p>对学生不伦的恋慕心，与对同床异梦夫妻关系的绝望，进退维谷间，有岛再次执笔创作。</p><p><img src="https://r2.touchgal.net/2023/05/98567c35b5102635.jpg"></img></p><p><img src="https://r2.touchgal.net/2023/05/781405fcc2102637.jpg"></img></p><hr><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/%E6%A2%93%E6%BE%AA%E5%A6%99%E5%A6%99%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%88zi0.cc%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90(gal%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90)/%60%E3%80%90%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E3%80%91/%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96galgame%E4%BC%9A%E7%A4%BE%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86/%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96%E4%BC%9A%E7%A4%BE%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%20part12/Laplacian/%5B200925%5D%5BLaplacian%5D%20%E7%99%BD%E6%98%BC%E5%A4%A2%E3%81%AE%E9%9D%92%E5%86%99%E7%9C%9F.rar"   title="PC"><i class="red larger"></i><span>PC</span></a><a class="btn-beautify " href="https://www.123pan.com/s/Xjvljv-lDBfv.html"   title="KR"><i class="red larger"></i><span>KR</span></a>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
