  <entry>
    <title>【PC】初恋预报。</title>
    <link href="https://yinghu.netlify.app/posts/b80fcb3.html"/>
    <id>https://yinghu.netlify.app/posts/b80fcb3.html</id>
    <published>2024-05-24T03:29:21.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-05-24T03:39:24.581Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>街道上布满层层积雪。<br>纯洁无瑕的白雪犹如一颗不被世俗污染的纯粹心灵。<br>轻轻一触碰，便会瞬间融化。<br>但是，积雪只会逐渐将这里染成一片银色的世界。<br>那么，恋人们又将如何渡过这个寒冷的冬季呢。<br>紧紧相依，迎接只属于两人的神圣之夜吗。<br>独自打拼的幸太郎心底的那份寂寞在忙碌的日常中消失殆尽。</p><p>完全无法预料，那样痛苦，快乐，彷徨的日子会降临他的生活。</p><p>甜美中带有些许忧伤的初恋。<br>幸太郎经历了一场让他永远无法忘怀的冬季之恋。</p><p><img src="https://r2.touchgal.net/2023/11/1167610aa120231110124508.jpg"></img></p><hr><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/%E6%A2%93%E6%BE%AA%E5%A6%99%E5%A6%99%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%88zi0.cc%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90(gal%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90)/%60%E3%80%90%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E3%80%91/%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96galgame%E4%BC%9A%E7%A4%BE%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86/%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96%E4%BC%9A%E7%A4%BE%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%20part11/I.D/%5B110527%5D%5BI.D.%5D%20%E5%88%9D%E6%81%8B%E4%BA%88%E5%A0%B1%E3%80%82.rar"   title="点击下载"><i class="red larger"></i><span>点击下载</span></a>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
